# ── Only track: MobileApp/, Model Code/, HuggingFace Space/, README.md ────────

# Ignore everything at the root level by default
/*

# Then explicitly allow only what we want
!MobileApp/
!Model Code/
!HuggingFace Space/
!README.md
!.gitignore

# Inside MobileApp — exclude generated/heavy folders
MobileApp/node_modules/
MobileApp/android/
MobileApp/ios/
MobileApp/.expo/
MobileApp/dist/

# Inside Model Code — exclude model weights and cache
Model Code/__pycache__/
Model Code/*.pyc
Model Code/ekman_emotion_model/
Model Code/.claude/

# Inside HuggingFace Space — exclude secrets
HuggingFace Space/.env

# System
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
